{
  "id": "adv_main_03_12_04",
  "title": "BIG4編1章59話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_big4-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 4.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-lmn001.m4a",
      "text": "さて、今日の配信で喋ることは大体……あら、電話？\nしかも……琴乃からね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ what I'm going to talk about in today's broadcast is about‚‚‚ Oh‚ a call?\nAnd‚‚‚ it’s from Kotono‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 7.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 11.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-lim001.m4a",
      "text": "……はっ。配信中だって分かってねぇのかよ\nそれとも……まぁいい。出てやれよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hah‚ Don't they know we're in the middle of a stream?\nOr…well‚ whatever‚ Answer it‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 20.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-lmn002.m4a",
      "text": "もしもし？　琴乃、久しぶりね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello? Kotono‚ it’s been a while‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 24.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "お久しぶりです。突然すみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s been a while‚ Sorry to call you so suddenly‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 28.6951246579
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-lim002.m4a",
      "text": "弱っちい負け犬がなんの用だよ\n今、配信中だって分かってんのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you losers want?\nDo you know we're in the middle of a broadcast?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.0284579913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.1717913246
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.1717913246
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "……はい、分かってます\n私達に興味がないという話も聞いていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes‚ I know‚\nI also heard that you’re not interested in us‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-lmn003.m4a",
      "text": "ふーん……なるほど。ふふ、正直でいいわねぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… I see‚ Fufu‚ it’s good to be honest‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.0257120133,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.8590453466
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-lim003.m4a",
      "text": "それで、なんの用だ？\nまさか……再戦してほしい、なんて言わねぇよな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ what’s your business?\nYou’re not going to ask us for a rematch…are you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.9923809688,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.2257120133
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、言わせてもらいます\n私達と……月ストと、もう一度戦って下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I’m going to ask‚\nPlease battle us again…Moon Tempest‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_contact-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 65.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-lim004.m4a",
      "text": "はっ！　本当にどうしようもないくらいのバカだな\nあたしらの話を聞いてたんだろうが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hah! You really are an idiot beyond help‚\nYou heard what we said‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.0592948914
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-lmn004.m4a",
      "text": "事務所経由で断られたからって直談判って訳？\n安直ねぇ。それでなんとかなると思ったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you’re making a direct appeal because you were rejected through your office?\nSo simple‚ Did you think it would work?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.0926282247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-lim005.m4a",
      "text": "結果の見えてる勝負なんてやる意味ないんだよ\nお前ら負け犬に割く時間なんかねぇんだ。切るぞ――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no point in a fight where the outcome is already obvious‚\nI don't have time for you losers‚ Hang up――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.5926305135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.692625173
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "――逃げるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Are you running away?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.692625173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_rival-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 96.6236667316
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-lim006.m4a",
      "text": "……あ？\nおい、もう一度言ってみろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What?\nOi‚ say that again‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.3903387387,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.8236667316
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、お望みなら何度でも言わせてもらいます\nあのどりきゅんが、これだけの人が見ている前で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I’ll say it as many times as you like‚\nThat DoriKyun‚ in front of so many people‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "何度も打ち負かした相手に宣戦布告されて……まさか\n尻尾を巻いて逃げ出すなんてこと……ないですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…being challenged to a rematch by an opponent they’ve defeated so many times…you wouldn’t…\n…turn tail and run‚ would you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 124.1757775307
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 124.1757775307
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-lmn005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……あははははは！\nなるほどねぇ、考えたじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu…ahahahaha!\nI see‚ You thought this through‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.4757805824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 132.2091177305
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-lmn006.m4a",
      "text": "普段からほうぼうに喧嘩を売ってる私達が、生配信中に\nこんな喧嘩を売られて。買わない訳ないわよねぇ、来夢",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We‚ who pick fights with everyone‚ being challenged like this in the middle of a live stream…\n…there’s no way we wouldn’t accept‚ right‚ Laim?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.6424472491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 141.9424510639
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-lim007.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだな。そこまでして潰されたいってことか\nいいぜ、やってやるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You’re right‚ So you want to be crushed that badly?\nAlright‚ we’ll do it‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.0263628296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.6424441974
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.6424441974
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 150.8367592495
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "……っ！　ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…G-Got it! Thank you very much!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.6424449604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.2816965104
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-lmn007.m4a",
      "text": "ただし……ちゃーんと牙を研いで\nこの前以上のものを見せてちょうだいね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However…make sure you sharpen your claws‚\nand show us something even better than last time‚ alright?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.2816987991,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.7150298437
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
