      "text": "望みは非常に薄い気はしますね\nそれはもう、非常に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have a feeling the chances are very slim‚\nVery…very slim‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 329.1642365854,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
