      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスとの合同練習についてなんだが……\n承諾してもらえたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "About the joint practice with IIIX…\n…they agreed‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 344.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "え……ほ、本当ですか！？\n絶対断られると思ってました……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh…R-Really!?\nI thought they’d definitely refuse…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 350.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "俺が直接三人に掛け合った時は即座に断られたんだよ\nだけど、あっさり引き下がれないと思ってな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I asked them directly‚ they refused immediately‚\nBut I couldn’t just back down‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それで三枝さんにも相談してみたら……mihoさん\nから、合同練習のスケジュールについて連絡がきたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ I talked to Saegusa-san too…and I got a message from Miho-san\nabout the joint practice schedule‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 364.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんは、一体どのような交渉をしたんでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What kind of negotiations did Saegusa-san make?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 367.9603693089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんは面白がって「受けた理由はスリクスから\n直接聞くといい」なんて言っててな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saegusa-san chuckled and said‚ “You can ask IIIX directly why they accepted‚”\n…so…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 376.6470964877,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと理由を聞くのが怖い気はしますけど……\nでも、これで道は開けましたね。練習頑張りましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m a little scared to ask why…\nBut at least we have a chance now‚ Let’s practice hard!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 384.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
