      "text": "ほ、本当に来ましたわ……！\nでも、なんであんなに機嫌が悪そうなんですの……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-They really came…!\nBut why do they look so grumpy…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 398.2259552083,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
