      "text": "来いって言ったのはそっちでしょ\nなのにその態度、もう帰っていいってことかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re the ones who asked us to come‚\nSo with that attitude‚ does that mean we can go home?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 405.8666076661,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
