      "text": "kana忙しいし、帰っていいなら帰るんですけどー\nお子様達の相手とか、マジめんどいし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kana’s busy‚ so I’ll go home if I can~\nDealing with kids is a real pain‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 414.6065219007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、すみません！\nそう言わずに、しばらくお付き合いいただけると……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry‚ I’m sorry!\nPlease‚ don’t say that‚ and just keep us company for a little while…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 419.7999409994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_04-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "二人の言うことは気にしなくていいですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don’t have to pay attention to what they’re saying‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 423.1749235236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
