      "text": "どれほど気に食わない仕事だろうと\n引き受けたからには、最後まできちんとやりますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No matter how much I hate a job‚\nonce I’ve accepted it‚ I’ll see it through to the end‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 428.6666076661,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
